data.title: Official Sega Dreamcast 10 Holiday 2000
data.meta_description: Official_Sega_Dreamcast_10_Holiday_2000 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides previews and information about upcoming video games for the Sega Dreamcast console. It highlights 16 titles across various genres including fighting games like Guilty Gear X and Soul Reaver 2; sports games like Coaster Works and Xtreme Sports; action games like Army Men Sarge's Heroes, Evil Dead 2, Bang! Gunship Elite, and Charge'n Blast; and RPGs like Skies of Arcadia and Grandia II. The previews describe the gameplay, storylines, features and release details for each title.
